$ Microsoft Store

*Microsoft Store* is a curated *digital distribution platform* for apps, console games and digital video.

Competitors offer similar functionality through *Google Play* or *Mac App Store*.

{ Sideloading

  The term *sideloading* refers to installing apps that haven't gone through the certification process (and thus don't show up in the Store).

  By default, → Windows does not allow to sideload apps.

